ide lucide-download h-4 w-4" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 15V3"></path><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4"></path><path d="m7 10 5 5 5-5"></path></svg></button><button aria-label="Close sidebar" class="flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg p-1.5 text-default-500 transition-colors hover:bg-default-100 hover:text-foreground dark:hover:bg-default-800" type="button" style="background-color: transparent;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-x h-5 w-5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M18 6 6 18"></path><path d="m6 6 12 12"></path></svg></button></div></div><div class="flex min-h-0 flex-1 overflow-y-auto overflow-x-hidden px-4 py-4"><div class="flex items-center justify-center py-8"><p class="text-default-500 text-sm">No file data available</p></div></div></div></div><div class="relative h-full min-h-0 min-w-0 flex-1"><div class="absolute inset-0 flex flex-col"><div class="w-full flex-grow overflow-y-auto overflow-x-hidden [scrollbar-gutter:stable_both-edges] chat-container px-2"><div class="mx-auto min-h-full w-full max-w-3xl px-0 pt-4"><div class="flex flex-col"><div class="flex flex-col"><div class="chat-message group/message w-full animate-message-enter chat-message-cv" data-role="user" data-testid="message-user"><div class="flex w-full min-w-full gap-4 group-data-[role=user]/message:ml-auto group-data-[role=user]/message:max-w-2xl group-data-[role=user]/message:justify-end mt-4 mb-3"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-2 items-end"><div role="user" class="relative flex gap-3 hyphens-none break-words max-w-[80%] self-end"><div class="flex w-full flex-col"><div class="relative w-full bg-[#F4F4F4] dark:bg-paper text-default-800 rounded-[14px] px-3 py-2 mb-6"><div data-testid="message-content"><div class="space-y-4 whitespace-normal *:first:mt-0 *:last:mb-0 chat-markdown max-w-none"><p>θελω να μου φτιαξεις εναν κωδικα για ενα παιχνιδι το οποιο θα βρισκεται online σε σελιδα</p></div></div></div><div class="-bottom-2 absolute right-0 transition-opacity duration-200"><div class="flex justify-end gap-1"><button class="message-action-button p-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-testid="user-copy-to-clipboard-button" type="button" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-copy" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="14" height="14" x="8" y="8" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><path d="M4 16c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V4c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h10c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2"></path></svg></button></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="chat-message group/message w-full animate-message-enter chat-message-cv" data-role="assistant" data-testid="message-assistant"><div class="flex w-full min-w-full gap-4 group-data-[role=user]/message:ml-auto group-data-[role=user]/message:max-w-2xl group-data-[role=user]/message:justify-end mt-4 mb-3"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-2"><div class="w-full max-w-full overflow-hidden"><div class="px-1 [overflow-wrap:anywhere] [word-break:break-word] websearch-response-content"><div class="space-y-4 whitespace-normal *:first:mt-0 *:last:mb-0 chat-markdown max-w-none"><p>Τέλεια! Για να σου φτιάξω τον κατάλληλο κώδικα, χρειάζομαι λίγες πληροφορίες:</p>
<p><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Τι είδους παιχνίδι έχεις στο μυαλό σου;</span></p>
<p>Μερικά παραδείγματα:</p>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Arcade</span> (π.χ. Snake, Tetris, Space Invaders)</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Quiz / Trivia</span></li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Παιχνίδι καρτών</span></li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Puzzle</span> (π.χ. Memory, Sudoku)</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Clicker / Idle game</span></li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Multiplayer</span> (π.χ. Tic-tac-toe με άλλους παίκτες)</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Text-based RPG / Adventure</span></li>
</ul>
<p>Επίσης, πες μου:</p>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Θα παίζεται <span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">μόνος</span> ή <span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">με άλλους παίκτες</span> online;</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Έχεις κάποια προτίμηση σε τεχνολογία; (HTML/CSS/JavaScript είναι το standard για browser games)</li>
</ul>
<p>Περίγραψέ μου την ιδέα σου και θα σου δώσω έναν λειτουργικό κώδικα!</p></div></div><div class="flex flex-col gap-2 mt-3"><div class="flex flex-col gap-2 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:gap-3"><div class="order-2 sm:order-1"><div class="flex gap-1"><button class="message-action-button p-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-testid="copy-to-clipboard-button" type="button" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-copy h-[17px] w-[17px] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-200" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="14" height="14" x="8" y="8" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><path d="M4 16c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V4c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h10c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2"></path></svg></button><button class="message-action-button p-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-testid="message-upvote" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-thumbs-up h-[17px] w-[17px] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M15 5.88 14 10h5.83a2 2 0 0 1 1.92 2.56l-2.33 8A2 2 0 0 1 17.5 22H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2.76a2 2 0 0 0 1.79-1.11L12 2a3.13 3.13 0 0 1 3 3.88Z"></path><path d="M7 10v12"></path></svg></button><button class="message-action-button p-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-testid="message-downvote" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-thumbs-down h-[17px] w-[17px] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M9 18.12 10 14H4.17a2 2 0 0 1-1.92-2.56l2.33-8A2 2 0 0 1 6.5 2H20a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v8a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-2.76a2 2 0 0 0-1.79 1.11L12 22a3.13 3.13 0 0 1-3-3.88Z"></path><path d="M17 14V2"></path></svg></button></div></div><button class="justify-center whitespace-nowrap font-medium transition-all duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-1 focus-visible:ring-ring disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg]:size-[18px] [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 min-h-[40px] hover:opacity-80 px-4 order-1 flex h-[38px] w-fit cursor-default items-center gap-1.5 rounded-3xl border border-border bg-transparent py-2 ps-3 pe-3 text-dark text-xs hover:border-semidark sm:order-2 dark:text-foreground dark:hover:border-gray-500"><div class="flex items-center"><div class="relative size-4 overflow-hidden rounded-full"><img alt="freelancer.gr" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" src="./map_europe_states_files/favicons" style="position: absolute; height: 100%; width: 100%; inset: 0px; color: transparent;"></div></div>5 Πηγές</button></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="chat-message group/message w-full animate-message-enter chat-message-cv" data-role="user" data-testid="message-user"><div class="flex w-full min-w-full gap-4 group-data-[role=user]/message:ml-auto group-data-[role=user]/message:max-w-2xl group-data-[role=user]/message:justify-end mt-4 mb-3"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-2 items-end"><div role="user" class="relative flex gap-3 hyphens-none break-words max-w-[80%] self-end"><div class="flex w-full flex-col"><div class="relative w-full bg-[#F4F4F4] dark:bg-paper text-default-800 rounded-[14px] px-3 py-2 mb-6"><div data-testid="message-content"><div class="space-y-4 whitespace-normal *:first:mt-0 *:last:mb-0 chat-markdown max-w-none"><p>θελω να ειναι ενα clicker σαν το worldbox ή το openfront το οποιο ειναι στρατηγικης θα φτιαχνεις το χωριο σου και θα εχεις επιλογες να φτιαξεις σπιτια για αυξξηση πληθυσμου λιμανι για να κανεις εμποριο καθως και barracks για να μπορεις να φτιαχνεις στρατο με τον εναπομειναντα πληθυσμο θα φτιαχνεις πρωτες υλες που θα ειναι χρησιμες για την αγορα ολων αυτω παραπανω ενω θα χρησιμοποιησεις τον χαρτη της ευρωπης</p></div></div></div><div class="-bottom-2 absolute right-0 transition-opacity duration-200"><div class="flex justify-end gap-1"><button class="message-action-button p-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-testid="user-copy-to-clipboard-button" type="button" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-copy" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="14" height="14" x="8" y="8" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><path d="M4 16c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V4c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h10c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2"></path></svg></button></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="chat-message group/message w-full animate-message-enter chat-message-cv" data-role="assistant" data-testid="message-assistant"><div class="flex w-full min-w-full gap-4 group-data-[role=user]/message:ml-auto group-data-[role=user]/message:max-w-2xl group-data-[role=user]/message:justify-end mt-4 mb-3"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-2"><div role="assistant" class="relative flex gap-3 hyphens-none break-words"><div class="flex w-full flex-col"><div class="relative w-full pb-8"><div data-testid="message-content"><div class="space-y-4 whitespace-normal *:first:mt-0 *:last:mb-0 chat-markdown max-w-none"><p>Μπορείς να το στήσεις ως <span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">απλό clicker/strategy hybrid</span> με ξεκάθαρα συστήματα. Να μια σύντομη, λειτουργική βάση για το παιχνίδι σου:</p>
<h2 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-2xl" data-streamdown="heading-2">Πυρήνας Παιχνιδιού</h2>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Click → Παράγεις βασικούς πόρους</span> (ξύλο, πέτρα, φαγητό, χρυσό).</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Χρήση πόρων → Χτίζεις κτίρια</span> που ξεκλειδώνουν παθητική παραγωγή, πληθυσμό και στρατό.</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Πληθυσμός → Κατανέμεται</span> σε εργάτες ή στρατιώτες.</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Χάρτης Ευρώπης → Περιοχές</span> που κατακτάς ή κάνεις εμπόριο.</li>
</ul>
<hr class="my-6 border-border" data-streamdown="horizontal-rule">
<h2 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-2xl" data-streamdown="heading-2">Κτίρια</h2>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Σπίτια</span>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Κόστος: ξύλο + πέτρα</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Δίνει: αύξηση μέγιστου πληθυσμού ανά λεπτό</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Λιμάνι</span>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Κόστος: ξύλο + χρυσό</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Δίνει: εμπόριο (αυτόματα bonus πόρων κάθε Χ δευτερόλεπτα)</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Barracks</span>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Κόστος: πέτρα + χρυσό</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Δίνει: δυνατότητα να μετατρέπεις πληθυσμό σε στρατιώτες</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Εργαστήρια / Μύλοι / Λατομεία</span>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Αυξάνουν παθητικά την παραγωγή πόρων</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<hr class="my-6 border-border" data-streamdown="horizontal-rule">
<h2 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-2xl" data-streamdown="heading-2">Πληθυσμός</h2>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Total population = villagers + soldiers</span></li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Villagers</span> → χρησιμοποιούνται για παραγωγή πόρων</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Soldiers</span> → χρησιμοποιούνται για επέκταση στον χάρτη της Ευρώπης</li>
</ul>
<hr class="my-6 border-border" data-streamdown="horizontal-rule">
<h2 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-2xl" data-streamdown="heading-2">Στρατός &amp; Κατάκτηση</h2>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Κάθε περιοχή της Ευρώπης έχει:
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Εχθρική δύναμη</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Loot σε πόρους</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Bonus μόλις κατακτηθεί (π.χ. Γαλλία → +20% παραγωγή ξύλου)</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Ο στρατός σου έχει:
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Αριθμό στρατιωτών</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Επίπεδο/αναβάθμιση damage και defense</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<hr class="my-6 border-border" data-streamdown="horizontal-rule">
<h2 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-2xl" data-streamdown="heading-2">Προτάσεις Progression</h2>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Tier 1</span>: βασικοί πόροι + σπίτια</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Tier 2</span>: λιμάνι + εμπόριο</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Tier 3</span>: barracks + στρατός</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Tier 4</span>: conquest όλων των χωρών της Ευρώπης</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Prestige/Rebirth</span>: ξεκινάς ξανά με μόνιμα bonus</li>
</ul>
<hr class="my-6 border-border" data-streamdown="horizontal-rule">
<h2 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-2xl" data-streamdown="heading-2">Χάρτης Ευρώπης</h2>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Απλό grid με χώρες ως “nodes”</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Κάθε node ξεκλειδώνεται με νίκη</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Δίνει μοναδικό passive bonus</li>
</ul>
<hr class="my-6 border-border" data-streamdown="horizontal-rule">
<p>Αν θέλεις, μπορώ να σου φτιάξω:</p>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">αναλυτικό game loop,</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">πίνακα ισορροπίας (costs, numbers),</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">pseudo-code,</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">UI layout,</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">ή πλήρες GDD (Game Design Document).</li>
</ul></div></div></div><div class="absolute bottom-0 transition-opacity duration-200 left-0"><div class="flex gap-1"><button class="message-action-button p-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-testid="copy-to-clipboard-button" type="button" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-copy h-[17px] w-[17px] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-200" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="14" height="14" x="8" y="8" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><path d="M4 16c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V4c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h10c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2"></path></svg></button><button class="message-action-button p-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-testid="message-upvote" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-thumbs-up h-[17px] w-[17px] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M15 5.88 14 10h5.83a2 2 0 0 1 1.92 2.56l-2.33 8A2 2 0 0 1 17.5 22H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2.76a2 2 0 0 0 1.79-1.11L12 2a3.13 3.13 0 0 1 3 3.88Z"></path><path d="M7 10v12"></path></svg></button><button class="message-action-button p-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-testid="message-downvote" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-thumbs-down h-[17px] w-[17px] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M9 18.12 10 14H4.17a2 2 0 0 1-1.92-2.56l2.33-8A2 2 0 0 1 6.5 2H20a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v8a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-2.76a2 2 0 0 0-1.79 1.11L12 22a3.13 3.13 0 0 1-3-3.88Z"></path><path d="M17 14V2"></path></svg></button></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="chat-message g