-normal *:first:mt-0 *:last:mb-0 chat-markdown max-w-none"><p>Τέλεια — δώσε μου τον πλήρη τιμοκατάλογο και θα τον ενσωματώσω αμέσως στο σύστημα του παιχνιδιού σου.</p></div></div></div><div class="absolute bottom-0 transition-opacity duration-200 left-0"><div class="flex gap-1"><button class="message-action-button p-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-testid="copy-to-clipboard-button" type="button" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-copy h-[17px] w-[17px] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-200" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="14" height="14" x="8" y="8" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><path d="M4 16c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V4c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h10c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2"></path></svg></button><button class="message-action-button p-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-testid="message-upvote" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-thumbs-up h-[17px] w-[17px] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M15 5.88 14 10h5.83a2 2 0 0 1 1.92 2.56l-2.33 8A2 2 0 0 1 17.5 22H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2.76a2 2 0 0 0 1.79-1.11L12 2a3.13 3.13 0 0 1 3 3.88Z"></path><path d="M7 10v12"></path></svg></button><button class="message-action-button p-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-testid="message-downvote" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-thumbs-down h-[17px] w-[17px] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M9 18.12 10 14H4.17a2 2 0 0 1-1.92-2.56l2.33-8A2 2 0 0 1 6.5 2H20a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v8a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-2.76a2 2 0 0 0-1.79 1.11L12 22a3.13 3.13 0 0 1-3-3.88Z"></path><path d="M17 14V2"></path></svg></button></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="chat-message group/message w-full animate-message-enter chat-message-cv" data-role="user" data-testid="message-user"><div class="flex w-full min-w-full gap-4 group-data-[role=user]/message:ml-auto group-data-[role=user]/message:max-w-2xl group-data-[role=user]/message:justify-end mt-4 mb-3"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-2 items-end"><div role="user" class="relative flex gap-3 hyphens-none break-words max-w-[80%] self-end"><div class="flex w-full flex-col"><div class="relative w-full bg-[#F4F4F4] dark:bg-paper text-default-800 rounded-[14px] px-3 py-2 mb-6"><div data-testid="message-content"><div class="space-y-4 whitespace-normal *:first:mt-0 *:last:mb-0 chat-markdown max-w-none"><p>καθε παικτης θα ξεκιναει με 10 gold ο καθε εργατης θα κοστιζει</p></div></div></div><div class="-bottom-2 absolute right-0 transition-opacity duration-200"><div class="flex justify-end gap-1"><button class="message-action-button p-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-testid="user-copy-to-clipboard-button" type="button" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-copy" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="14" height="14" x="8" y="8" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><path d="M4 16c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V4c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h10c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2"></path></svg></button></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="chat-message group/message w-full animate-message-enter chat-message-cv" data-role="assistant" data-testid="message-assistant"><div class="flex w-full min-w-full gap-4 group-data-[role=user]/message:ml-auto group-data-[role=user]/message:max-w-2xl group-data-[role=user]/message:justify-end mt-4 mb-3"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-2"><div role="assistant" class="relative flex gap-3 hyphens-none break-words"><div class="flex w-full flex-col"><div class="relative w-full pb-8"><div data-testid="message-content"><div class="space-y-4 whitespace-normal *:first:mt-0 *:last:mb-0 chat-markdown max-w-none"><p>Πες μου το κόστος του κάθε εργάτη για να το προσθέσω σωστά στον τιμοκατάλογο.</p></div></div></div><div class="absolute bottom-0 transition-opacity duration-200 left-0"><div class="flex gap-1"><button class="message-action-button p-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-testid="copy-to-clipboard-button" type="button" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-copy h-[17px] w-[17px] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-200" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="14" height="14" x="8" y="8" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><path d="M4 16c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V4c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h10c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2"></path></svg></button><button class="message-action-button p-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-testid="message-upvote" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-thumbs-up h-[17px] w-[17px] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M15 5.88 14 10h5.83a2 2 0 0 1 1.92 2.56l-2.33 8A2 2 0 0 1 17.5 22H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2.76a2 2 0 0 0 1.79-1.11L12 2a3.13 3.13 0 0 1 3 3.88Z"></path><path d="M7 10v12"></path></svg></button><button class="message-action-button p-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-testid="message-downvote" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-thumbs-down h-[17px] w-[17px] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M9 18.12 10 14H4.17a2 2 0 0 1-1.92-2.56l2.33-8A2 2 0 0 1 6.5 2H20a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v8a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-2.76a2 2 0 0 0-1.79 1.11L12 22a3.13 3.13 0 0 1-3-3.88Z"></path><path d="M17 14V2"></path></svg></button></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="chat-message group/message w-full animate-message-enter chat-message-cv" data-role="user" data-testid="message-user"><div class="flex w-full min-w-full gap-4 group-data-[role=user]/message:ml-auto group-data-[role=user]/message:max-w-2xl group-data-[role=user]/message:justify-end mt-4 mb-3"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-2 items-end"><div role="user" class="relative flex gap-3 hyphens-none break-words max-w-[80%] self-end"><div class="flex w-full flex-col"><div class="relative w-full bg-[#F4F4F4] dark:bg-paper text-default-800 rounded-[14px] px-3 py-2 mb-6"><div data-testid="message-content"><div class="space-y-4 whitespace-normal *:first:mt-0 *:last:mb-0 chat-markdown max-w-none"><p>Κάθε εργάτης θα κοστίζει 3 gold, κάθε λιμάνι 8 και κάθε barracks θα κοστίζει 15.</p></div></div></div><div class="-bottom-2 absolute right-0 transition-opacity duration-200"><div class="flex justify-end gap-1"><button class="message-action-button p-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-testid="user-copy-to-clipboard-button" type="button" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-copy" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="14" height="14" x="8" y="8" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><path d="M4 16c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V4c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h10c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2"></path></svg></button></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="chat-message group/message w-full animate-message-enter chat-message-cv" data-role="assistant" data-testid="message-assistant"><div class="flex w-full min-w-full gap-4 group-data-[role=user]/message:ml-auto group-data-[role=user]/message:max-w-2xl group-data-[role=user]/message:justify-end mt-4 mb-3"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-2"><div role="assistant" class="relative flex gap-3 hyphens-none break-words"><div class="flex w-full flex-col"><div class="relative w-full pb-8"><div data-testid="message-content"><div class="space-y-4 whitespace-normal *:first:mt-0 *:last:mb-0 chat-markdown max-w-none"><p>Ορίστε ο ενημερωμένος βασικός τιμοκατάλογος, βασισμένος σε όσα έδωσες:</p>
<p><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Αρχικά δεδομένα</span></p>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Ξεκινάς με 10 gold.</li>
</ul>
<p><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Κόστη μονάδων και κτιρίων</span></p>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Εργάτης: 3 gold</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Λιμάνι: 8 gold</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Barracks: 15 gold</li>
</ul>
<p>Αν θέλεις, μπορώ να σου φτιάξω τώρα:</p>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">αναλυτικό economy balance,</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">πώς θα γίνεται το scaling όταν ο παίκτης προχωράει,</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">ή πλήρη τιμοκατάλογο με όλα τα κτίρια/πόρους/αναβαθμίσεις.</li>
</ul></div></div></div><div class="absolute bottom-0 transition-opacity duration-200 left-0"><div class="flex gap-1"><button class="message-action-button p-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-testid="copy-to-clipboard-button" type="button" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-copy h-[17px] w-[17px] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-200" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="14" height="14" x="8" y="8" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><path d="M4 16c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V4c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h10c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2"></path></svg></button><button class="message-action-button p-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-testid="message-upvote" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-thumbs-up h-[17px] w-[17px] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M15 5.88 14 10h5.83a2 2 0 0 1 1.92 2.56l-2.33 8A2 2 0 0 1 17.5 22H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2.76a2 2 0 0 0 1.79-1.11L12 2a3.13 3.13 0 0 1 3 3.88Z"></path><path d="M7 10v12"></path></svg></button><button class="message-action-button p-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-testid="message-downvote" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-thumbs-down h-[17px] w-[17px] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M9 18.12 10 14H4.17a2 2 0 0 1-1.92-2.56l2.33-8A2 2 0 0 1 6.5 2H20a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v8a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-2.76a2 2 0 0 0-1.79 1.11L12 22a3.13 3.13 0 0 1-3-3.88Z"></path><path d="M17 14V2"></path></svg></button></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="chat-message group/message w-full animate-message-enter chat-message-cv" data-role="user" data-testid="message-user"><div class="flex w-full min-w-full gap-4 group-data-[role=user]/message:ml-auto group-data-[role=user]/message:max-w-2xl group-data-[role=user]/message:justify-end mt-4 mb-3"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-2 items-end"><div role="user" class="relative flex gap-3 hyphens-none break-words max-w-[80%] self-end"><div class="flex w-full flex-col"><div class="relative w-full bg-[#F4F4F4] dark:bg-paper text-default-800 rounded-[14px] px-3 py-2 mb-6"><div data-testid="message-content"><div class="space-y-4 whitespace-normal *:first:mt-0 *:last:mb-0 chat-markdown max-w-none"><p>ναι προτεινε μου ενα</p></div></div></div><div class="-bottom-2 absolute right-0 transition-opacity duration-200"><div class="flex justify-end gap-1"><button class="message-action-button p-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-testid="user-copy-to-clipboard-button" type="button" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-copy" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="14" height="14" x="8" y="8" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><path d="M4 16c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V4c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h10c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2"></path></svg></button></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="chat-message group/message w-full animate-message-enter chat-message-cv" data-role="assistant" data-testid="message-assistant"><div class="flex w-full min-w-full gap-4 group-data-[role=user]/message:ml-auto group-data-[role=user]/message:max-w-2xl group-data-[role=user]/message:justify-end mt-4 mb-3"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-2"><div role="assistant" class="relative flex gap-3 hyphens-none break-words"><div class="flex w-full flex-col"><div class="relative w-full pb-8"><div data-testid="message-content"><div class="space-y-4 whitespace-normal *:first:mt-0 *:last:mb-0 chat-markdown max-w-none"><p>Ορίστε μια καθαρή, ολοκληρωμένη οικονομία (economy balance) που ταιριάζει απόλυτα στο clicker/strategy στυλ που χτίζεις. Κρατάει το gameplay γρήγορο στην αρχή, αλλά με ωραίο scaling όσο προχωρά ο παίκτης.</p>
<h2 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-2xl" data-streamdown="heading-2">Οικονομία Παιχνιδιού (Πρόταση)</h2>
<h3 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-xl" data-streamdown="heading-3">Βασικοί Πόροι</h3>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Gold</span>: κύριο νόμισμα για αγορά κτιρίων/εργατών.</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Wood</span>: απαραίτητο για βασικά κτίρια.</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Stone</span>: προχωρημένα κτίρια.</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Food</span>: αυξάνει πληθυσμό και ταχύτητα παραγωγής.</li>
</ul>
<p>Το gold μπορεί να είναι ο μόνος πόρος στην αρχή για απλότητα, και να ξεκλειδώνεις τους υπόλοιπους με progression.</p>
<hr class="my-6 border-border" data-streamdown="horizontal-rule">
<h2 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-2xl" data-streamdown="heading-2">Κόστη Μονάδων &amp; Κτιρίων (με scaling)</h2>
<h3 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-xl" data-streamdown="heading-3">Εργάτης</h3>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Αρχικό κόστος:</span> 3 gold</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Αύξηση κόστους:</span> +0.5 gold ανά αγορά (ώστε να μη γίνεται spam)</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Λειτουργία:</span> +1 passive παραγωγή σε έναν βασικό πόρο (π.χ. wood)</li>
</ul>
<h3 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-xl" data-streamdown="heading-3">Σπίτι</h3>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Αρχικό κόστος:</span> 5 wood</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Αύξηση κόστους:</span> +2 wood ανά επίπεδο</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Λειτουργία:</span> +4 μέγιστος πληθυσμός</li>
</ul>
<h3 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-xl" data-streamdown="heading-3">Λιμάνι (Port)</h3>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Αρχικό κόστος:</span> 8 gold</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Αύξηση κόστους:</span> +3 gold ανά κατασκευή</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Λειτουργία:</span> αυτόματη παραγωγή gold ανά λεπτό (π.χ. +2/min)</li>
</ul>
<h3 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-xl" data-streamdown="heading-3">Barracks</h3>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Αρχικό κόστος:</span> 15 gold</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Αύξηση κόστους:</span> +5 gold ανά κατασκευή</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Λειτουργία:</span> δυνατότητα στρατολόγησης στρατιωτών από διαθέσιμο πληθυσμό</li>
</ul>
<h3 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-xl" data-streamdown="heading-3">Στρατιώτης</h3>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Κόστος σε πληθυσμό:</span> 1 villager</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Κόστος σε πόρο:</span> 2 food + 1 stone</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Λειτουργία:</span> χρησιμοποιείται για μάχες στον χάρτη</li>
</ul>
<hr class="my-6 border-border" data-streamdown="horizontal-rule">
<h2 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-2xl" data-streamdown="heading-2">Συστήματα Scaling (σημαντικό για clicker)</h2>
<p>Για να είναι διασκεδαστικό:</p>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Τα passive κέρδη (Wood, Stone, Gold ανά λεπτό) αυξάνουν <span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">εκθετικά</span> όσο χτίζεις.</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Τα κόστη αυξάνουν <span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">γραμμικά</span> ή <span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">ήπια εκθετικά</span>.</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Η πρόοδος στις περιοχές της Ευρώπης δίνει <span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">permanent bonuses</span>.</li>
</ul>
<hr class="my-6 border-border" data-streamdown="horizontal-rule">
<h2 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-2xl" data-streamdown="heading-2">Bonus από Κατακτημένες Περιοχές</h2>
<p>Κάθε χώρα δίνει ένα μικρό “μεταλλικό” bonus:</p>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Ελλάδα: +10% παραγωγή food</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Ιταλία: +5% παραγωγή gold</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Γαλλία: +15% wood</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Γερμανία: +10% stone</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Ισπανία: +20% speed στα passive ticks</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Σκανδιναβία: +15% παραγωγή όλων των πόρων αλλά -10% αύξηση πληθυσμού</li>
</ul>
<p>(Μπορώ να σου φτιάξω και πλήρη λίστα για όλες τις χώρες.)</p>
<hr class="my-6 border-border" data-streamdown="horizontal-rule">
<h2 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-2xl" data-streamdown="heading-2">Loop Παιχνιδιού</h2>
<ol class="list-inside list-decimal whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="ordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Ο παίκτης κλικάρει για gold.</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Αγοράζει εργάτες → αυξάνει παθητική παραγωγή.</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Χτίζει σπίτια → αυξάνει πληθυσμό.</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Χτίζει λιμάνι → αυξάνει gold/min.</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Χτίζει barracks → στρατολογεί.</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Κατακτά χώρες → παίρνει μόνιμα bonuses.</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Επαναλαμβάνει με scaling.</li>
</ol>
<hr class="my-6 border-border" data-streamdown="horizontal-rule">
<p>Αν θες, μπορώ να σου γράψω:</p>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">πλήρες <span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">GDD</span>,</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">pseudocode</span> για το economy loop,</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">UI mockup</span>,</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">ή <span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">JSON/ScriptableObjects</span> για Unity.</li>
</ul></div></div></div><div class="absolute bottom-0 transition-opacity duration-200 left-0"><div class="flex gap-1"><button class="message-action-button p-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-testid="copy-to-clipboard-button" type="button" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-copy h-[17px] w-[17px] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-200" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="14" height="14" x="8" y="8" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><path d="M4 16c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V4c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h10c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2"></path></svg></button><button class="message-action-button p-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-testid="message-upvote" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-thumbs-up h-[17px] w-[17px] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M15 5.88 14 10h5.83a2 2 0 0 1 1.92 2.56l-2.33 8A2 2 0 0 1 17.5 22H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2.76a2 2 0 0 0 1.79-1.11L12 2a3.13 3.13 0 0 1 3 3.88Z"></path><path d="M7 10v12"></path></svg></button><button class="message-action-button p-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-testid="message-downvote" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-thumbs-down h-[17px] w-[17px] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M9 18.12 10 14H4.17a2 2 0 0 1-1.92-2.56l2.33-8A2 2 0 0 1 6.5 2H20a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v8a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-2.76a2 2 0 0 0-1.79 1.11L12 22a3.13 3.13 0 0 1-3-3.88Z"></path><path d="M17 14V2"></path></svg></button></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="chat-message group/message w-full animate-message-enter chat-message-cv" data-role="user" data-testid="message-user"><div class="flex w-full min-w-full gap-4 group-data-[role=user]/message:ml-auto group-data-[role=user]/message:max-w-2xl group-data-[role=user]/message:justify-end mt-4 mb-3"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-2 items-end"><div role="user" class="relative flex gap-3 hyphens-none break-words max-w-[80%] self-end"><div class="flex w-full flex-col"><div class="relative w-full bg-[#F4F4F4] dark:bg-paper text-default-800 rounded-[14px] px-3 py-2 mb-6"><div data-testid="message-content"><div class="space-y-4 whitespace-normal *:first:mt-0 *:last:mb-0 chat-markdown max-w-none"><p>φτιαξτο</p></div></div></div><div class="-bottom-2 absolute right-0 transition-opacity duration-200"><div class="flex justify-end gap-1"><button class="message-action-button p-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-testid="user-copy-to-clipboard-button" type="button" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-copy" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="14" height="14" x="8" y="8" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><path d="M4 16c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V4c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h10c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2"></path></svg></button></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="chat-message group/message w-full animate-message-enter chat-message-cv" data-role="assistant" data-testid="message-assistant"><div class="flex w-full min-w-full gap-4 group-data-[role=user]/message:ml-auto group-data-[role=user]/message:max-w-2xl group-data-[role=user]/message:justify-end mt-4 mb-3"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-2"><div role="assistant" class="relative flex gap-3 hyphens-none break-words"><div class="flex w-full flex-col"><div class="relative w-full pb-8"><div data-testid="message-content"><div class="space-y-4 whitespace-normal *:first:mt-0 *:last:mb-0 chat-markdown max-w-none"><p>Ορίστε ένα πλήρες, καθαρό <span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">GDD (Game Design Document)</span> βασισμένο σε όσα ζητήσαμε και συμφωνήσαμε μέχρι τώρα. Είναι έτοιμο για ανάπτυξη.</p>
<hr class="my-6 border-border" data-streamdown="horizontal-rule">
<h1 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-3xl" data-streamdown="heading-1">Game Design Document</h1>
<p><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Τίτλος:</span> <em>EU Clicker Conquest</em><br>
<span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Είδος:</span> Clicker / Incremental Strategy<br>
<span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Χάρτης:</span> Ευρώπη<br>
<span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Πυρήνας:</span> Χτίζεις χωριό → χτίζεις οικονομία → φτιάχνεις στρατό → κατακτάς χώρες της Ευρώπης</p>
<hr class="my-6 border-border" data-streamdown="horizontal-rule">
<h2 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-2xl" data-streamdown="heading-2">1. Αρχικά Στοιχεία</h2>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Ο παίκτης ξεκινάει με <span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">10 gold</span>.</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Καμία άλλη δομή χτισμένη.</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Κλικ → παράγει 1 gold (base).</li>
</ul>
<hr class="my-6 border-border" data-streamdown="horizontal-rule">
<h2 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-2xl" data-streamdown="heading-2">2. Πόροι</h2>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Gold:</span> βασικό νόμισμα για αγορές.</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Wood:</span> χρησιμοποιείται για σπίτια και εργαστήρια.</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Stone:</span> για προχωρημένα κτίρια.</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Food:</span> για αύξηση πληθυσμού και στρατιώτες.</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Population:</span> χωρίζεται σε Villagers &amp; Soldiers.</li>
</ul>
<hr class="my-6 border-border" data-streamdown="horizontal-rule">
<h2 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-2xl" data-streamdown="heading-2">3. Μονάδες &amp; Κτίρια</h2>
<h3 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-xl" data-streamdown="heading-3">Εργάτης (Villager)</h3>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Κόστος: <span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">3 gold</span></li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Αύξηση κόστους: +0.5 gold ανά εργάτη</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Παράγει: +1 wood/min (ή άλλον πόρο ανά assignment)</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Καταλαμβάνει 1 μονάδα πληθυσμού</li>
</ul>
<hr class="my-6 border-border" data-streamdown="horizontal-rule">
<h3 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-xl" data-streamdown="heading-3">Σπίτι (House)</h3>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Κόστος: 5 wood</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Αύξηση κόστους: +2 wood</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Δίνει: +4 μέγιστο πληθυσμό</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Παθητικό bonus: +0.1 food/min</li>
</ul>
<hr class="my-6 border-border" data-streamdown="horizontal-rule">
<h3 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-xl" data-streamdown="heading-3">Λιμάνι (Port)</h3>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Κόστος: <span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">8 gold</span></li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Αύξηση κόστους: +3 gold</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Παράγει: +2 gold/min</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Ξεκλειδώνει: Σύστημα εμπορίου (trade upgrades)</li>
</ul>
<hr class="my-6 border-border" data-streamdown="horizontal-rule">
<h3 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-xl" data-streamdown="heading-3">Barracks</h3>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Κόστος: <span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">15 gold</span></li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Αύξηση κόστους: +5 gold</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Δίνει δυνατότητα εκπαίδευσης στρατιωτών</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Παθητικό: +10% ταχύτερος χρόνος εκπαίδευσης</li>
</ul>
<hr class="my-6 border-border" data-streamdown="horizontal-rule">
<h3 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-xl" data-streamdown="heading-3">Στρατιώτης (Soldier)</h3>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Κόστος: 1 population (villager → soldier)</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Απαιτεί: 2 food + 1 stone</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Ισχύς: 1 attack power</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Χρήση: Κατακτά περιοχές</li>
</ul>
<hr class="my-6 border-border" data-streamdown="horizontal-rule">
<h3 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-xl" data-streamdown="heading-3">Παραγωγικά κτίρια</h3>
<p><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Woodcutter’s Hut</span></p>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Κόστος: 10 wood</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Παράγει: +3 wood/min</li>
</ul>
<p><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Stone Quarry</span></p>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Κόστος: 15 wood</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Παράγει: +2 stone/min</li>
</ul>
<p><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Farm</span></p>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Κόστος: 10 wood</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Παράγει: +3 food/min</li>
</ul>
<hr class="my-6 border-border" data-streamdown="horizontal-rule">
<h2 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-2xl" data-streamdown="heading-2">4. Progression</h2>
<p>Το παιχνίδι εξελίσσεται σε tiers:</p>
<h3 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-xl" data-streamdown="heading-3">Tier 1</h3>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Κλικ → gold</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Αγορά εργάτη</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Σπίτια</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Χωρίς κατακτήσεις</li>
</ul>
<h3 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-xl" data-streamdown="heading-3">Tier 2</h3>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Λιμάνι</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Passive gold παραγωγή</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Trade bonuses</li>
</ul>
<h3 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-xl" data-streamdown="heading-3">Tier 3</h3>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Barracks</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Στρατολόγηση</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Επιθέσεις σε μικρές χώρες (Βαλκάνια)</li>
</ul>
<h3 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-xl" data-streamdown="heading-3">Tier 4</h3>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Drop σε κεντρική Ευρώπη</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Μεγάλες χώρες → μεγάλα bonuses</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Εκθετικό scaling παραγωγής</li>
</ul>
<hr class="my-6 border-border" data-streamdown="horizontal-rule">
<h2 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-2xl" data-streamdown="heading-2">5. Κατάκτηση Ευρώπης</h2>
<p>Κάθε χώρα έχει:</p>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Αμυντική δύναμη</span> (enemy power)</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Loot</span> (πόροι)</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Μόνιμο bonus</span></li>
</ul>
<p>Παράδειγμα bonus χωρών:</p>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Ελλάδα: +10% food production</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Ιταλία: +5% gold production</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Γαλλία: +15% wood production</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Γερμανία: +10% stone</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Ισπανία: +20% passive tick speed</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Σκανδιναβία: +15% σε όλους τους πόρους, -10% population growth</li>
</ul>
<p>Μπορώ να σου φτιάξω <span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">ολόκληρο τον χάρτη της Ευρώπης με όλα τα country stats</span> αν θέλεις.</p>
<hr class="my-6 border-border" data-streamdown="horizontal-rule">
<h2 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-2xl" data-streamdown="heading-2">6. Εμπορικό Σύστημα (Trade)</h2>
<p>Ξεκλειδώνει με το Λιμάνι.</p>
<p>Trades:</p>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">10 wood → 3 gold</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">5 stone → 7 gold</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">10 food → 1 military power bonus</li>
</ul>
<p>Με αναβαθμίσεις:</p>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">+5% trade efficiency per upgrade</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Κόστος upgrade: 25 gold → scaling +15%</li>
</ul>
<hr class="my-6 border-border" data-streamdown="horizontal-rule">
<h2 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-2xl" data-streamdown="heading-2">7. Prestige / Rebirth</h2>
<p>Όταν ο παίκτης κατακτήσει 10 χώρες:</p>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Μπορεί να κάνει <span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Rebirth</span></li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Παίρνει μόνιμο multiplier: +10% σε όλους τους πόρους</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Χάνει όλες τις κατακτήσεις αλλά κρατά το multiplier</li>
</ul>
<hr class="my-6 border-border" data-streamdown="horizontal-rule">
<h2 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-2xl" data-streamdown="heading-2">8. Game Loop</h2>
<ol class="list-inside list-decimal whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="ordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Κλικάρεις για gold</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Αγοράζεις εργάτες</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Χτίζεις σπίτια → αυξάνεις πληθυσμό</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Χτίζεις παραγωγικά κτίρια → scaling</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Φτιάχνεις στρατό</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Κατακτάς χώρες</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Ξεκλειδώνεις νέα bonuses</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Το παιχνίδι γίνεται σταδιακά full idle</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Rebirth για μόνιμα buffs</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Επαναλαμβάνεις</li>
</ol>
<hr class="my-6 border-border" data-streamdown="horizontal-rule">
<p>Αν θέλεις, μπορώ άμεσα να δημιουργήσω:</p>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">JSON data για όλα τα κτίρια &amp; μονάδες (έτοιμο για Unity / Godot)</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Τον πλήρη χάρτη της Ευρώπης με δύναμη–loot–bonus για 44 χώρες</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">UI design (layout για κλικ, resources, map, upgrades)</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Core gameplay pseudocode</li>
</ul>
<p>Τι από αυτά θες επόμενο;</p></div></div></div><div class="absolute bottom-0 transition-opacity duration-200 left-0"><div class="flex gap-1"><button class="message-action-button p-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-testid="copy-to-clipboard-button" type="button" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-copy h-[17px] w-[17px] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-200" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="14" height="14" x="8" y="8" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><path d="M4 16c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V4c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h10c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2"></path></svg></button><button class="message-action-button p-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-testid="message-upvote" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-thumbs-up h-[17px] w-[17px] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M15 5.88 14 10h5.83a2 2 0 0 1 1.92 2.56l-2.33 8A2 2 0 0 1 17.5 22H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2.76a2 2 0 0 0 1.79-1.11L12 2a3.13 3.13 0 0 1 3 3.88Z"></path><path d="M7 10v12"></path></svg></button><button class="message-action-button p-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-testid="message-downvote" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-thumbs-down h-[17px] w-[17px] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M9 18.12 10 14H4.17a2 2 0 0 1-1.92-2.56l2.33-8A2 2 0 0 1 6.5 2H20a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v8a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-2.76a2 2 0 0 0-1.79 1.11L12 22a3.13 3.13 0 0 1-3-3.88Z"></path><path d="M17 14V2"></path></svg></button></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>