="relative w-full pb-8"><div data-testid="message-content"><div class="space-y-4 whitespace-normal *:first:mt-0 *:last:mb-0 chat-markdown max-w-none"><p>Το προσθέτω στο σύστημα κατάκτησης με τρόπο που ταιριάζει τέλεια στο clicker–strategy gameplay σου.</p>
<h2 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-2xl" data-streamdown="heading-2">Σύστημα Μάχης &amp; Κατάκτησης (με διπλό κλικ)</h2>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Κάθε χώρα στον χάρτη της Ευρώπης εμφανίζεται ως <span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">interactive region</span>.</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Ο παίκτης πρέπει να κάνει <span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">διπλό κλικ</span> σε μια χώρα.</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Με το δεύτερο κλικ ξεκινάει άμεσα η μάχη.</li>
</ul>
<hr class="my-6 border-border" data-streamdown="horizontal-rule">
<h2 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-2xl" data-streamdown="heading-2">Ροή Μάχης (Battle Flow)</h2>
<ol class="list-inside list-decimal whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="ordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Ο παίκτης κάνει διπλό κλικ</span> στο εικονίδιο της χώρας.</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Εμφανίζεται παράθυρο:
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Enemy Power (π.χ. 30)</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Your Army Power (άθροισμα στρατιωτών × power)</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Reward (πόροι + μόνιμο bonus)</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Κουμπί: <span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Attack</span></li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Αυτόματη μάχη:
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Αν ArmyPower ≥ EnemyPower → Νίκη</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Αν ArmyPower &lt; EnemyPower → Ήττα (χάνεις 10–30% στρατό)</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ol>
<hr class="my-6 border-border" data-streamdown="horizontal-rule">
<h2 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-2xl" data-streamdown="heading-2">Τι συμβαίνει σε Νίκη</h2>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Κατακτάς τη χώρα.</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Παίρνεις τα loot resources.</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Ενεργοποιείται το passive bonus της χώρας για πάντα.</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Η χώρα αλλάζει χρώμα/κατάσταση στο χάρτη.</li>
</ul>
<hr class="my-6 border-border" data-streamdown="horizontal-rule">
<h2 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-2xl" data-streamdown="heading-2">Τι συμβαίνει σε Ήττα</h2>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Χάνεις μέρος του στρατού.</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Η χώρα γίνεται προσωρινά “locked” για 30 sec (anti-spam).</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Παίρνεις μήνυμα “Army not strong enough”.</li>
</ul>
<hr class="my-6 border-border" data-streamdown="horizontal-rule">
<h2 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-2xl" data-streamdown="heading-2">Quality of Life</h2>
<p>Για να νιώθει clicker:</p>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Δείξε μικρό animation στο διπλό κλικ (π.χ. pulse).</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Άμεσο feedback: highlight της χώρας.</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Χρήσιμο tooltip: power level, bonus, κλπ.</li>
</ul>
<hr class="my-6 border-border" data-streamdown="horizontal-rule">
<p>Αν θέλεις, μπορώ να σου φτιάξω τώρα:</p>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Τον πλήρη πίνακα όλων των χωρών της Ευρώπης</span> με power, loot και bonus</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Ή <span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">pseudocode</span> για το σύστημα διπλού κλικ + μάχη</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Ή <span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">UI layout</span> για τον χάρτη και το attack window</li>
</ul></div></div></div><div class="absolute bottom-0 transition-opacity duration-200 left-0"><div class="flex gap-1"><button class="message-action-button p-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-testid="copy-to-clipboard-button" type="button" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-copy h-[17px] w-[17px] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-200" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="14" height="14" x="8" y="8" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><path d="M4 16c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V4c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h10c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2"></path></svg></button><button class="message-action-button p-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-testid="message-upvote" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-thumbs-up h-[17px] w-[17px] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M15 5.88 14 10h5.83a2 2 0 0 1 1.92 2.56l-2.33 8A2 2 0 0 1 17.5 22H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2.76a2 2 0 0 0 1.79-1.11L12 2a3.13 3.13 0 0 1 3 3.88Z"></path><path d="M7 10v12"></path></svg></button><button class="message-action-button p-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-testid="message-downvote" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-thumbs-down h-[17px] w-[17px] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M9 18.12 10 14H4.17a2 2 0 0 1-1.92-2.56l2.33-8A2 2 0 0 1 6.5 2H20a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v8a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-2.76a2 2 0 0 0-1.79 1.11L12 22a3.13 3.13 0 0 1-3-3.88Z"></path><path d="M17 14V2"></path></svg></button></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="chat-message group/message w-full animate-message-enter chat-message-cv" data-role="user" data-testid="message-user"><div class="flex w-full min-w-full gap-4 group-data-[role=user]/message:ml-auto group-data-[role=user]/message:max-w-2xl group-data-[role=user]/message:justify-end mt-4 mb-3"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-2 items-end"><div role="user" class="relative flex gap-3 hyphens-none break-words max-w-[80%] self-end"><div class="flex w-full flex-col"><div class="relative w-full bg-[#F4F4F4] dark:bg-paper text-default-800 rounded-[14px] px-3 py-2 mb-6"><div data-testid="message-content"><div class="space-y-4 whitespace-normal *:first:mt-0 *:last:mb-0 chat-markdown max-w-none"><p>φτιαξε ναι</p></div></div></div><div class="-bottom-2 absolute right-0 transition-opacity duration-200"><div class="flex justify-end gap-1"><button class="message-action-button p-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-testid="user-copy-to-clipboard-button" type="button" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-copy" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="14" height="14" x="8" y="8" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><path d="M4 16c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V4c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h10c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2"></path></svg></button></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="chat-message group/message w-full animate-message-enter chat-message-cv" data-role="assistant" data-testid="message-assistant"><div class="flex w-full min-w-full gap-4 group-data-[role=user]/message:ml-auto group-data-[role=user]/message:max-w-2xl group-data-[role=user]/message:justify-end mt-4 mb-3"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-2"><div role="assistant" class="relative flex gap-3 hyphens-none break-words"><div class="flex w-full flex-col"><div class="relative w-full pb-8"><div data-testid="message-content"><div class="space-y-4 whitespace-normal *:first:mt-0 *:last:mb-0 chat-markdown max-w-none"><p>Παρακάτω σου φτιάχνω <span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">τον πλήρη πίνακα κατάκτησης χωρών της Ευρώπης</span> με:</p>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Enemy Power</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Loot που δίνουν</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Μόνιμο Bonus όταν τις κατακτήσεις</li>
</ul>
<p>Ο πίνακας είναι σχεδιασμένος για clicker–strategy balance: μικρές χώρες εύκολες, μεγάλες χώρες δύσκολες αλλά με μεγαλύτερα bonuses.</p>
<hr class="my-6 border-border" data-streamdown="horizontal-rule">
<h1 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-3xl" data-streamdown="heading-1">Πίνακας Κατάκτησης Ευρώπης</h1>
