<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">JSON αρχεία</span> με όλα τα stats των χωρών</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">UI layout για τη μάχη</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">scaling μαθηματικά για enemy power &amp; army power</li>
</ul>
<p>Τι θες να δώσω επόμενο;</p></div></div></div><div class="absolute bottom-0 transition-opacity duration-200 left-0"><div class="flex gap-1"><button class="message-action-button p-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-testid="copy-to-clipboard-button" type="button" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-copy h-[17px] w-[17px] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-200" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="14" height="14" x="8" y="8" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><path d="M4 16c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V4c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h10c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2"></path></svg></button><button class="message-action-button p-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-testid="message-upvote" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-thumbs-up h-[17px] w-[17px] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M15 5.88 14 10h5.83a2 2 0 0 1 1.92 2.56l-2.33 8A2 2 0 0 1 17.5 22H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2.76a2 2 0 0 0 1.79-1.11L12 2a3.13 3.13 0 0 1 3 3.88Z"></path><path d="M7 10v12"></path></svg></button><button class="message-action-button p-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-testid="message-downvote" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-thumbs-down h-[17px] w-[17px] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M9 18.12 10 14H4.17a2 2 0 0 1-1.92-2.56l2.33-8A2 2 0 0 1 6.5 2H20a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v8a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-2.76a2 2 0 0 0-1.79 1.11L12 22a3.13 3.13 0 0 1-3-3.88Z"></path><path d="M17 14V2"></path></svg></button></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="chat-message group/message w-full animate-message-enter chat-message-cv" data-role="user" data-testid="message-user"><div class="flex w-full min-w-full gap-4 group-data-[role=user]/message:ml-auto group-data-[role=user]/message:max-w-2xl group-data-[role=user]/message:justify-end mt-4 mb-3"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-2 items-end"><div role="user" class="relative flex gap-3 hyphens-none break-words max-w-[80%] self-end"><div class="flex w-full flex-col"><div class="relative w-full bg-[#F4F4F4] dark:bg-paper text-default-800 rounded-[14px] px-3 py-2 mb-6"><div data-testid="message-content"><div class="space-y-4 whitespace-normal *:first:mt-0 *:last:mb-0 chat-markdown max-w-none"><p>ui layout</p></div></div></div><div class="-bottom-2 absolute right-0 transition-opacity duration-200"><div class="flex justify-end gap-1"><button class="message-action-button p-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-testid="user-copy-to-clipboard-button" type="button" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-copy" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="14" height="14" x="8" y="8" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><path d="M4 16c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V4c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h10c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2"></path></svg></button></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="chat-message group/message w-full animate-message-enter chat-message-cv" data-role="assistant" data-testid="message-assistant"><div class="flex w-full min-w-full gap-4 group-data-[role=user]/message:ml-auto group-data-[role=user]/message:max-w-2xl group-data-[role=user]/message:justify-end mt-4 mb-3"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-2"><div role="assistant" class="relative flex gap-3 hyphens-none break-words"><div class="flex w-full flex-col"><div class="relative w-full pb-8"><div data-testid="message-content"><div class="space-y-4 whitespace-normal *:first:mt-0 *:last:mb-0 chat-markdown max-w-none"><p>Παρακάτω είναι ένα καθαρό, λειτουργικό <span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">UI layout</span> για το παιχνίδι σου, σχεδιασμένο για απλότητα, ευκολία χρήσης και clicker/strategy ροή.</p>
<hr class="my-6 border-border" data-streamdown="horizontal-rule">
<h1 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-3xl" data-streamdown="heading-1">UI Layout</h1>
<h2 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-2xl" data-streamdown="heading-2">1. Επάνω Μπάρα (Top HUD)</h2>
<p><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Περιέχει όλους τους πόρους:</span></p>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Gold</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Wood</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Stone</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Food</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Population (Villagers / Cap)</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Soldiers</li>
</ul>
<p>Δεξιά:</p>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Passive Production Rate (π.χ. +12/min)</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Tick Speed Icon</li>
</ul>
<p>Η μπάρα είναι πάντα ορατή.</p>
<hr class="my-6 border-border" data-streamdown="horizontal-rule">
<h2 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-2xl" data-streamdown="heading-2">2. Κεντρική Περιοχή (Main Panel)</h2>
<p>Αλλάζει ανά tab:</p>
<h3 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-xl" data-streamdown="heading-3">A. <span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Village View</span></h3>
<p>Στο κέντρο εμφανίζεται το χωριό με κτίρια ως κουμπιά:</p>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">House</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Woodcutter</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Quarry</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Farm</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Port</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Barracks</li>
</ul>
<p>Κάθε κτίριο:</p>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">εικονίδιο</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">κόστος</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">επίπεδο</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">παραγωγή</li>
</ul>
<p>Κλικάροντας τα κτίρια ανοίγει δεξί πίνακας (Info Panel).</p>
<hr class="my-6 border-border" data-streamdown="horizontal-rule">
<h3 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-xl" data-streamdown="heading-3">B. <span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Map View</span> (Χάρτης Ευρώπης)</h3>
<p>Ο χάρτης καταλαμβάνει όλο το κέντρο.</p>
<p>Επικράτειες:</p>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Χρώμα γκρι = μη κατακτημένες</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Πράσινο = δικές σου</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Κόκκινο highlight όταν κάνεις hover</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Διπλό κλικ → εμφανίζει Battle Window</li>
</ul>
<hr class="my-6 border-border" data-streamdown="horizontal-rule">
<h3 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-xl" data-streamdown="heading-3">C. <span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Army View</span></h3>
<p>Λίστα:</p>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Στρατιώτες διαθέσιμοι</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Training Queue</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Κουμπί Train Soldier</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">στατιστικά στρατού (attack, defense)</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<p>Bar κάτω:</p>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Training progress bar</li>
</ul>
<hr class="my-6 border-border" data-streamdown="horizontal-rule">
<h3 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-xl" data-streamdown="heading-3">D. <span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Trade View</span></h3>
<p>Κουπόνια:</p>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Convert Wood → Gold</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Convert Stone → Gold</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Convert Food → Military Boost</li>
</ul>
<p>Κάθε κουμπί:</p>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">κόστος</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">αποτέλεσμα</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">cooldown</li>
</ul>
<hr class="my-6 border-border" data-streamdown="horizontal-rule">
<h2 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-2xl" data-streamdown="heading-2">3. Κάτω Μπάρα (Navigation Tabs)</h2>
<p>Πάντα ορατή:</p>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Village</span></li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Army</span></li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Map</span></li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Trade</span></li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Upgrades</span></li>
</ul>
<hr class="my-6 border-border" data-streamdown="horizontal-rule">
<h2 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-2xl" data-streamdown="heading-2">4. Δεξί Πλαϊνό Πάνελ (Info Panel)</h2>
<p>Ανοίγει δυναμικά όταν επιλέγεις ένα κτίριο ή χώρα:</p>
<p>Εμφανίζει:</p>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Όνομα</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Περιγραφή</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Κόστος</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Παραγωγή</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Next Level Stats</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Κουμπί “Build” ή “Upgrade”</li>
</ul>
<p>Όταν επιλέγεις χώρα:</p>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Enemy Power</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Loot</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Bonus</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Κουμπί Attack (0.5 sec delay μετά το διπλό κλικ)</li>
</ul>
<hr class="my-6 border-border" data-streamdown="horizontal-rule">
<h2 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-2xl" data-streamdown="heading-2">5. Battle Window (popup)</h2>
<p>Εμφανίζεται μετά το διπλό κλικ στη χώρα:</p>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Εικονίδιο χώρας</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Enemy Power</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Your Army Power</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Ενδεικτική μπάρα “Win chance”</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Button: <span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Attack</span></li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Tooltip: Loss Penalty</li>
</ul>
<p>Μετά τη μάχη:</p>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Popup “Victory” ή “Defeat”</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Loot / Losses</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Κουμπί Close</li>
</ul>
<hr class="my-6 border-border" data-streamdown="horizontal-rule">
<h2 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-2xl" data-streamdown="heading-2">6. Bottom Right – Quick Actions</h2>
<p>Μικρά κουμπιά:</p>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Train Soldier (γρήγορη πρόσβαση)</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Build House</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Build Worker</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Open Upgrades</li>
</ul>
<hr class="my-6 border-border" data-streamdown="horizontal-rule">
<h2 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-2xl" data-streamdown="heading-2">7. Left Side – Notifications</h2>
<p>Μικρά notifications που εμφανίζονται και εξαφανίζονται:</p>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">“+2 Gold (Port income)”</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">“House built”</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">“You conquered Italy!”</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">“Not enough resources”</li>
</ul>
<hr class="my-6 border-border" data-streamdown="horizontal-rule">
<p>Αν θέλεις, μπορώ να σου φτιάξω τώρα:</p>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">UI mockup περιγραφικό ανά οθόνη</span></li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">UI mockup σε ASCII σχήμα</span></li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">UI flowchart</span></li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">ή έτοιμο layout για Unity UI Toolkit / Canvas.</li>
