ιμη και μπορείς να τη χρησιμοποιήσεις ως προσχέδιο για το UI. Αν θες, μπορώ να σου ετοιμάσω και μια δεύτερη εκδοχή του mockup με διαφορετική διάταξη (π.χ. Map View αντί για Village View).</p></div></div></div><div class="absolute bottom-0 transition-opacity duration-200 left-0"><div class="flex gap-1"><button class="message-action-button p-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-testid="copy-to-clipboard-button" type="button" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-copy h-[17px] w-[17px] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-200" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="14" height="14" x="8" y="8" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><path d="M4 16c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V4c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h10c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2"></path></svg></button><button class="message-action-button p-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-testid="message-upvote" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-thumbs-up h-[17px] w-[17px] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M15 5.88 14 10h5.83a2 2 0 0 1 1.92 2.56l-2.33 8A2 2 0 0 1 17.5 22H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2.76a2 2 0 0 0 1.79-1.11L12 2a3.13 3.13 0 0 1 3 3.88Z"></path><path d="M7 10v12"></path></svg></button><button class="message-action-button p-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-testid="message-downvote" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-thumbs-down h-[17px] w-[17px] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M9 18.12 10 14H4.17a2 2 0 0 1-1.92-2.56l2.33-8A2 2 0 0 1 6.5 2H20a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v8a2