lass="chat-message group/message w-full animate-message-enter chat-message-cv" data-role="user" data-testid="message-user"><div class="flex w-full min-w-full gap-4 group-data-[role=user]/message:ml-auto group-data-[role=user]/message:max-w-2xl group-data-[role=user]/message:justify-end mt-4 mb-3"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-2 items-end"><div role="user" class="relative flex gap-3 hyphens-none break-words max-w-[80%] self-end"><div class="flex w-full flex-col"><div class="relative w-full bg-[#F4F4F4] dark:bg-paper text-default-800 rounded-[14px] px-3 py-2 mb-6"><div data-testid="message-content"><div class="space-y-4 whitespace-normal *:first:mt-0 *:last:mb-0 chat-markdown max-w-none"><p>λιστα μπονους</p></div></div></div><div class="-bottom-2 absolute right-0 transition-opacity duration-200"><div class="flex justify-end gap-1"><button class="message-action-button p-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-testid="user-copy-to-clipboard-button" type="button" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-copy" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="14" height="14" x="8" y="8" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><path d="M4 16c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V4c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h10c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2"></path></svg></button></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="chat-message group/message w-full animate-message-enter chat-message-cv" data-role="assistant" data-testid="message-assistant"><div class="flex w-full min-w-full gap-4 group-data-[role=user]/message:ml-auto group-data-[role=user]/message:max-w-2xl group-data-[role=user]/message:justify-end mt-4 mb-3"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-2"><div role="assistant" class="relative flex gap-3 hyphens-none break-words"><div class="flex w-full flex-col"><div class="relative w-full pb-8"><div data-testid="message-content"><div class="space-y-4 whitespace-normal *:first:mt-0 *:last:mb-0 chat-markdown max-w-none"><p>Ορίστε η πλήρης, καθαρή και ισορροπημένη <span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">λίστα bonuses για κάθε κρατίδιο</span>, βασισμένη στο bonus της χώρας-μητέρας.<br>
Το bonus της χώρας <span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">μοιράζεται στα κρατίδια</span>, ώστε κάθε περιοχή να δίνει ένα <span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">κομμάτι</span> του συνολικού bonus.<br>
Κάθε χώρα εξακολουθεί να έχει το <span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">ίδιο συνολικό bonus</span>, απλώς “σπάει” σε μικρότερα partial buffs.</p>
<hr class="my-6 border-border" data-streamdown="horizontal-rule">
<h1 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-3xl" data-streamdown="heading-1">Bonus Ανά Χώρα &amp; Κρατίδιο</h1>
<h2 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-2xl" data-streamdown="heading-2">Μεγάλες χώρες</h2>
<h3 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-xl" data-streamdown="heading-3">Γαλλία – Συνολικό bonus: <span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">+15% wood production</span> (5 κρατίδια → +3% το καθένα)</h3>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">France North → +3% wood</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">France South → +3% wood</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">France East → +3% wood</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">France West → +3% wood</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">France Central → +3% wood</li>
</ul>
<h3 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-xl" data-streamdown="heading-3">Γερμανία – Συνολικό bonus: <span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">+10% stone</span> (5 → +2% το καθένα)</h3>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Germany North → +2% stone</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Germany South → +2% stone</li>
