</ul></div></div></div><div class="absolute bottom-0 transition-opacity duration-200 left-0"><div class="flex gap-1"><button class="message-action-button p-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-testid="copy-to-clipboard-button" type="button" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-copy h-[17px] w-[17px] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-200" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="14" height="14" x="8" y="8" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><path d="M4 16c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V4c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h10c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2"></path></svg></button><button class="message-action-button p-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-testid="message-upvote" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-thumbs-up h-[17px] w-[17px] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M15 5.88 14 10h5.83a2 2 0 0 1 1.92 2.56l-2.33 8A2 2 0 0 1 17.5 22H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2.76a2 2 0 0 0 1.79-1.11L12 2a3.13 3.13 0 0 1 3 3.88Z"></path><path d="M7 10v12"></path></svg></button><button class="message-action-button p-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-testid="message-downvote" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-thumbs-down h-[17px] w-[17px] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M9 18.12 10 14H4.17a2 2 0 0 1-1.92-2.56l2.33-8A2 2 0 0 1 6.5 2H20a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v8a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-2.76a2 2 0 0 0-1.79 1.11L12 22a3.13 3.13 0 0 1-3-3.88Z"></path><path d="M17 14V2"></path></svg></button></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="chat-message group/message w-full animate-message-enter chat-message-cv" data-role="user" data-testid="message-user"><div class="flex w-full min-w-full gap-4 group-data-[role=user]/message:ml-auto group-data-[role=user]/message:max-w-2xl group-data-[role=user]/message:justify-end mt-4 mb-3"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-2 items-end"><div role="user" class="relative flex gap-3 hyphens-none break-words max-w-[80%] self-end"><div class="flex w-full flex-col"><div class="relative w-full bg-[#F4F4F4] dark:bg-paper text-default-800 rounded-[14px] px-3 py-2 mb-6"><div data-testid="message-content"><div class="space-y-4 whitespace-normal *:first:mt-0 *:last:mb-0 chat-markdown max-w-none"><p>δεν θελω special rare loot</p></div></div></div><div class="-bottom-2 absolute right-0 transition-opacity duration-200"><div class="flex justify-end gap-1"><button class="message-action-button p-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-testid="user-copy-to-clipboard-button" type="button" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-copy" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="14" height="14" x="8" y="8" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><path d="M4 16c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V4c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h10c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2"></path></svg></button></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="chat-message group/message w-full animate-message-enter chat-message-cv" data-role="assistant" data-testid="message-assistant"><div class="flex w-full min-w-full gap-4 group-data-[role=user]/message:ml-auto group-data-[role=user]/message:max-w-2xl group-data-[role=user]/message:justify-end mt-4 mb-3"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-2"><div role="assistant" class="relative flex gap-3 hyphens-none break-words"><div class="flex w-full flex-col"><div class="relative w-full pb-8"><div data-testid="message-content"><div class="space-y-4 whitespace-normal *:first:mt-0 *:last:mb-0 chat-markdown max-w-none"><p>Κανένα πρόβλημα — το σύστημα loot μένει <span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">καθαρό, σταθερό και χωρίς rare drops</span>.<br>
Όλα τα κρατίδια δίνουν μόνο:</p>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">βασικούς πόρους (wood, stone, food, gold)</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">ειδικούς πόρους όπου χρειάζεται (πχ weapons)</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">και τα bonus τους</li>
</ul>
<p>χωρίς RNG, χωρίς ειδικά αντικείμενα.</p>
<p>Αυτό κρατάει το παιχνίδι <span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">στρατηγικό και προβλέψιμο</span>, όχι τυχερό.</p>
<p>Αν θες, τώρα μπορώ να συνεχίσω με:</p>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">το <span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">JSON data pack</span> του loot table,<br>
ή</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">το <span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">σύστημα παραγωγής πόρων per tick</span> που θα δένει με τα bonuses και τα loot.</li>
</ul></div></div></div><div class="absolute bottom-0 transition-opacity duration-200 left-0"><div class="flex gap-1"><button class="message-action-button p-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-testid="copy-to-clipboard-button" type="button" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-copy h-[17px] w-[17px] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-200" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="14" height="14" x="8" y="8" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><path d="M4 16c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V4c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h10c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2"></path></svg></button><button class="message-action-button p-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-testid="message-upvote" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-thumbs-up h-[17px] w-[17px] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M15 5.88 14 10h5.83a2 2 0 0 1 1.92 2.56l-2.33 8A2 2 0 0 1 17.5 22H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2.76a2 2 0 0 0 1.79-1.11L12 2a3.13 3.13 0 0 1 3 3.88Z"></path><path d="M7 10v12"></path></svg></button><button class="message-action-button p-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-testid="message-downvote" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-thumbs-down h-[17px] w-[17px] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M9 18.12 10 14H4.17a2 2 0 0 1-1.92-2.56l2.33-8A2 2 0 0 1 6.5 2H20a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v8a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-2.76a2 2 0 0 0-1.79 1.11L12 22a3.13 3.13 0 0 1-3-3.88Z"></path><path d="M17 14V2"></path></svg></button></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="chat-message group/message w-full animate-message-enter chat-message-cv" data-role="user" data-testid="message-user"><div class="flex w-full min-w-full gap-4 group-data-[role=user]/message:ml-auto group-data-[role=user]/message:max-w-2xl group-data-[role=user]/message:justify-end mt-4 mb-3"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-2 items-end"><div role="user" class="relative flex gap-3 hyphens-none break-words max-w-[80%] self-end"><div class="flex w-full flex-col"><div class="relative w-full bg-[#F4F4F4] dark:bg-paper text-default-800 rounded-[14px] px-3 py-2 mb-6"><div data-testid="message-content"><div class="space-y-4 whitespace-normal *:first:mt-0 *:last:mb-0 chat-markdown max-w-none"><p>σύστημα παραγωγής πόρων per tick</p></div></div></div><div class="-bottom-2 absolute right-0 transition-opacity duration-200"><div class="flex justify-end gap-1"><button class="message-action-button p-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-testid="user-copy-to-clipboard-button" type="button" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-copy" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="14" height="14" x="8" y="8" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><path d="M4 16c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V4c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h10c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2"></path></svg></button></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="chat-message group/message w-full animate-message-enter chat-message-cv" data-role="assistant" data-testid="message-assistant"><div class="flex w-full min-w-full gap-4 group-data-[role=user]/message:ml-auto group-data-[role=user]/message:max-w-2xl group-data-[role=user]/message:justify-end mt-4 mb-3"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-2"><div role="assistant" class="relative flex gap-3 hyphens-none break-words"><div class="flex w-full flex-col"><div class="relative w-full pb-8"><div data-testid="message-content"><div class="space-y-4 whitespace-normal *:first:mt-0 *:last:mb-0 chat-markdown max-w-none"><p>Παρακάτω είναι ένα καθαρό, ισορροπημένο και πλήρως λειτουργικό <span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">σύστημα παραγωγής πόρων per tick</span>, το οποίο συνδέει:</p>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">την παραγωγή κτιρίων,</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">τους εργάτες,</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">τα bonuses κρατιδίων,</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">τα all‑resource bonuses,</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">τα debuffs,</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">και το tick speed.</li>
</ul>
<p>Αυτό είναι το core loop που θα τρέχει κάθε tick (π.χ. κάθε 1 δευτερόλεπτο ή 0.5 sec).</p>
<hr class="my-6 border-border" data-streamdown="horizontal-rule">
<h1 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-3xl" data-streamdown="heading-1">1. Ορισμός Tick</h1>
<p><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Ένα tick = 1 "κύκλος" παραγωγής.</span></p>
<p>Μπορεί να είναι:</p>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">1 δευτερόλεπτο (default)</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">ή 0.5 sec αν ο παίκτης πάρει bonus tick speed (π.χ. Ισπανία)</li>
</ul>
<hr class="my-6 border-border" data-streamdown="horizontal-rule">
<h1 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-3xl" data-streamdown="heading-1">2. Βασική Παραγωγή Ανά Τύπο Πόρου</h1>
<h2 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-2xl" data-streamdown="heading-2">Wood</h2>
<p>Wood per tick =<br>
(<span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Workers assigned to wood × 1</span>)</p>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">(κτίρια wood – όπως Woodcutters)</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">(country completion bonuses)</li>
</ul>
<h2 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-2xl" data-streamdown="heading-2">Stone</h2>
<p>Stone per tick =<br>
(<span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Workers assigned to stone × 1</span>)</p>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">(Quarries)</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">(country bonuses)</li>
</ul>
<h2 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-2xl" data-streamdown="heading-2">Food</h2>
<p>Food per tick =<br>
(<span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Workers assigned to food × 1</span>)</p>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">(Farms)</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">(food country bonuses)</li>
</ul>
<h2 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-2xl" data-streamdown="heading-2">Gold</h2>
<p>Gold per tick =</p>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">από κλικ</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">από ports</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">από passive bonuses (π.χ. UK)</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">από trade efficiency bonuses</li>
</ul>
<hr class="my-6 border-border" data-streamdown="horizontal-rule">
<h1 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-3xl" data-streamdown="heading-1">3. Γενικός Τύπος Παραγωγής (με bonuses)</h1>
<p>Για κάθε πόρο:</p>
<span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mrow><mtext>FinalProduction</mtext><mo>=</mo><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mtext>BaseProduction</mtext><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>×</mo><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mtext>TotalResourceBonus</mtext><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>×</mo><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mtext>AllResourcesBonus</mtext><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>×</mo><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mtext>TickSpeedMultiplier</mtext><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>×</mo><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mtext>Debuffs</mtext><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\text{FinalProduction} =
(\text{BaseProduction})
\times (1 + \text{TotalResourceBonus})
\times (1 + \text{AllResourcesBonus})
\times (\text{TickSpeedMultiplier})
\times (1 - \text{Debuffs})</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height: 0.6944em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">FinalProduction</span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right: 0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right: 0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height: 1em; vertical-align: -0.25em;"></span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">BaseProduction</span></span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right: 0.2222em;"></span><span class="mbin">×</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right: 0.2222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height: 1em; vertical-align: -0.25em;"></span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord">1</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right: 0.2222em;"></span><span class="mbin">+</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right: 0.2222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height: 1em; vertical-align: -0.25em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">TotalResourceBonus</span></span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right: 0.2222em;"></span><span class="mbin">×</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right: 0.2222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height: 1em; vertical-align: -0.25em;"></span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord">1</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right: 0.2222em;"></span><span class="mbin">+</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right: 0.2222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height: 1em; vertical-align: -0.25em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">AllResourcesBonus</span></span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right: 0.2222em;"></span><span class="mbin">×</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right: 0.2222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height: 1em; vertical-align: -0.25em;"></span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">TickSpeedMultiplier</span></span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right: 0.2222em;"></span><span class="mbin">×</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right: 0.2222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height: 1em; vertical-align: -0.25em;"></span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord">1</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right: 0.2222em;"></span><span class="mbin">−</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right: 0.2222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height: 1em; vertical-align: -0.25em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">Debuffs</span></span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span></span>
<p>Αναλυτικά:</p>
<h3 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-xl" data-streamdown="heading-3">BaseProduction</h3>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">workers × 1</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">buildings (farm, quarry, etc.)</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">prestige mods (αν υπάρχουν)</li>
</ul>
<h3 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-xl" data-streamdown="heading-3">TotalResourceBonus</h3>
<p>= άθροισμα όλων των bonuses από κρατίδια που δίνουν wood/stone/food/gold.</p>
<h3 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-xl" data-streamdown="heading-3">AllResourcesBonus</h3>
<p>= άθροισμα bonuses τύπου Russia, Sweden κλπ.</p>
<h3 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-xl" data-streamdown="heading-3">TickSpeedMultiplier</h3>
<p>=<br>
1.0 → normal<br>
1.05 → +5% από ένα ισπανικό κρατίδιο<br>
1.20 → αν έχει κατακτηθεί όλη η Ισπανία</p>
<p>Tick speed δεν επηρεάζει power, μόνο τη συχνότητα παραγωγής.</p>
<h3 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-xl" data-streamdown="heading-3">Debuffs</h3>
<p>= pop growth debuffs (π.χ. Σουηδία) + penalties που ίσως έχει ο παίκτης.</p>
<hr class="my-6 border-border" data-streamdown="horizontal-rule">
<h1 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-3xl" data-streamdown="heading-1">4. Παράδειγμα Πλήρους Tick Υπολογισμού</h1>
<h3 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-xl" data-streamdown="heading-3">Wood</h3>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">5 workers assigned</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">3 woodcutter huts → +6 wood</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Έχει κατακτήσει 2 γαλλικά κρατίδια → +6% wood</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Ένα μαροκινό → +2.5% wood</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Δύο ρωσικά → +8.32% all</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Tick speed από Ισπανία → +5%</li>
</ul>
<p>Υπολογισμός:</p>
<p>Base = 5 workers + 6 wood = <span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">11</span><br>
Wood bonus = 6% + 2.5% = <span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">8.5%</span><br>
Αll = 8.32%<br>
Tick speed = 1.05</p>
<p>Final:</p>
<p>11 × 1.085 × 1.0832 × 1.05 = <span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">13.54 wood/tick</span></p>
<hr class="my-6 border-border" data-streamdown="horizontal-rule">
<h1 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-3xl" data-streamdown="heading-1">5. Tick Speed Διαχείριση</h1>
<h3 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-xl" data-streamdown="heading-3">Normal tick</h3>
<p>tick = 1s</p>
<h3 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-xl" data-streamdown="heading-3">With Spanish bonuses</h3>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">1 κρατίδιο → tick = 0.95s</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">2 → 0.90s</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">3 → 0.85s</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">4 (όλη η Ισπανία) → 0.80s</li>
</ul>
<p>Tick time affects <em>frequency</em>, not production per tick.</p>
<hr class="my-6 border-border" data-streamdown="horizontal-rule">
<h1 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-3xl" data-streamdown="heading-1">6. Population Growth Tick</h1>
<p>Population growth per tick =<br>
( base growth ) × (1 + bonuses – debuffs)</p>
<p>Παράδειγμα:</p>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Base = 0.02 pop/tick</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">-3.3% from Sweden North</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">+3% from Kosovo</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Final = σχεδόν 0.02 pop/tick (ίσα βάρκα ίσα νερά)</li>
</ul>
<hr class="my-6 border-border" data-streamdown="horizontal-rule">
<h1 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-3xl" data-streamdown="heading-1">7. Gold per Tick</h1>
<p>Gold per tick =</p>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Port income</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">UK bonuses</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Trade bonuses</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">All‑resource bonuses</li>
</ul>
<p>Και φυσικά το clicker σύστημα δίνει +1–+2 gold per click.</p>
<hr class="my-6 border-border" data-streamdown="horizontal-rule">
<h1 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-3xl" data-streamdown="heading-1">8. Buildings Scaling</h1>
<p>Κάθε building μπορεί να έχει scaling:</p>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Woodcutter = +2 wood per level</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Quarry = +3 stone per level</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Farm = +3 food per level</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Port = +2 gold per minute per level</li>
</ul>
<p>Μπορώ να σου φτιάξω αναλυτικό balancing.</p>
<hr class="my-6 border-border" data-streamdown="horizontal-rule">
<h1 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-3xl" data-streamdown="heading-1">9. Upgrades (προαιρετικά)</h1>
<p>Upgrades προσθέτουν:</p>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">+10% συγκεκριμένο resource production</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">+5% all resources</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">+1 gold per click</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">+X tick speed</li>
</ul>
<p>και stackάρουν όπως τα bonuses των κρατιδίων.</p>
<hr class="my-6 border-border" data-streamdown="horizontal-rule">
<h3 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-xl" data-streamdown="heading-3">Αν θες μπορώ να φτιάξω τώρα:</h3>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Player Production Engine JSON</span> (όλα οι τύποι σε έτοιμο format)</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Production simulation</span> για test values</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Resource curve progression</span> (πότε φτάνεις σε 1000/10000 resources)</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Cost scaling system</span> για buildings &amp; workers</li>
</ul>
<p>Τι προχωράμε;</p></div></div></div><div class="absolute bottom-0 transition-opacity duration-200 left-0"><div class="flex gap-1"><button class="message-action-button p-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-testid="copy-to-clipboard-button" type="button" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-copy h-[17px] w-[17px] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-200" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="14" height="14" x="8" y="8" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><path d="M4 16c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V4c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h10c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2"></path></svg></button><button class="message-action-button p-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-testid="message-upvote" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-thumbs-up h-[17px] w-[17px] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M15 5.88 14 10h5.83a2 2 0 0 1 1.92 2.56l-2.33 8A2 2 0 0 1 17.5 22H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2.76a2 2 0 0 0 1.79-1.11L12 2a3.13 3.13 0 0 1 3 3.88Z"></path><path d="M7 10v12"></path></svg></button><button class="message-action-button p-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-testid="message-downvote" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-thumbs-down h-[17px] w-[17px] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M9 18.12 10 14H4.17a2 2 0 0 1-1.92-2.56l2.33-8A2 2 0 0 1 6.5 2H20a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v8a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-2.76a2 2 0 0 0-1.79 1.11L12 22a3.13 3.13 0 0 1-3-3.88Z"></path><path d="M17 14V2"></path></svg></button></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=