flat political map of Europe and northern Africa, where every country is subdivided into multiple small provinces. Each country’s provinces share the same color family (similar shades) but each province is a distinct color. Borders are precise and clear. The map fills almost the entire screen. At the top, there is a very small minimalist resource bar with tiny icons for gold, wood, stone, food, population, and soldiers, each followed by small counter numbers. No side panels or extra UI clutter. Modern, simple, strategy‑game style. in full screen" class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-[14px] cursor-pointer w-full" data-image-card="0" style="width: 100%; max-width: 100%; max-height: 600px; aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;"><img alt="A clean 2D game interface showing a flat political map of Europe and northern Africa, where every country is subdivided into multiple small provinces. Each country’s provinces share the same color family (similar shades) but each province is a distinct color. Borders are precise and clear. The map fills almost the entire screen. At the top, there is a very small minimalist resource bar with tiny icons for gold, wood, stone, food, population, and soldiers, each followed by small counter numbers. No side panels or extra UI clutter. Modern, simple, strategy‑game style." class="size-full scale-[1.15] rounded-[14px] object-cover transition-all duration-300" height="768" loading="lazy" width="1344" src="./map_europe_states_files/d556c941-333f-4d1a-be3e-7899640c5399-833564cb-ce4d-4c3f-879a-6421fab23371-1777662903263-0.png"><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/0 transition-all duration-200 group-hover:bg-black/20"><div class="absolute top-3 right-3 opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-200 group-hover:opacity-100"><button data-state="closed"><button class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap text-sm font-medium transition-all duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-1 focus-visible:ring-ring disabled:poi