<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">UI στοιχεία (κουμπιά, animations, tooltips)</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Mockup για μάχες (battle window)</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Mockup για upgrade menu</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">JSON δεδομένα για κρατίδια/χώρα/bonus/power/loot</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Ή ξεκινάμε να χτίζουμε τον actual κώδικα του παιχνιδιού</li>
</ul>
<p>Πες μου πώς θες να συνεχίσουμε.</p></div></div></div><div class="absolute bottom-0 transition-opacity duration-200 left-0"><div class="flex gap-1"><button class="message-action-button p-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-testid="copy-to-clipboard-button" type="button" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-copy h-[17px] w-[17px] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-200" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="14" height="14" x="8" y="8" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><path d="M4 16c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V4c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h10c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2"></path></svg></button><button class="message-action-button p-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-testid="message-upvote" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-thumbs-up h-[17px] w-[17px] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M15 5.88 14 10h5.83a2 2 0 0 1 1.92 2.56l-2.33 8A2 2 0 0 1 17.5 22H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2.76a2 2 0 0 0 1.79-1.11L12 2a3.13 3.13 0 0 1 3 3.88Z"></path><path d="M7 10v12"></path></svg></button><button class="message-action-button p-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-testid="message-downvote" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-thumbs-down h-[17px] w-[17px] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M9 18.12 10 14H4.17a2 2 0 0 1-1.92-2.56l2.33-8A2 2 0 0 1 6.5 2H20a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v8a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-2.76a2 2 0 0 0-1.79 1.11L12 22a3.13 3.13 0 0 1-3-3.88Z"></path><path d="M17 14V2"></path></svg></button></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="chat-message group/message w-full animate-message-enter chat-message-cv" data-role="user" data-testid="message-user"><div class="flex w-full min-w-full gap-4 group-data-[role=user]/message:ml-auto group-data-[role=user]/message:max-w-2xl group-data-[role=user]/message:justify-end mt-4 mb-3"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-2 items-end"><div role="user" class="relative flex gap-3 hyphens-none break-words max-w-[80%] self-end"><div class="flex w-full flex-col"><div class="relative w-full bg-[#F4F4F4] dark:bg-paper text-default-800 rounded-[14px] px-3 py-2 mb-6"><div data-testid="message-content"><div class="space-y-4 whitespace-normal *:first:mt-0 *:last:mb-0 chat-markdown max-w-none"><p>γραψε τον κωδικα</p></div></div></div><div class="-bottom-2 absolute right-0 transition-opacity duration-200"><div class="flex justify-end gap-1"><button class="message-action-button message-action-animate p-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-testid="user-copy-to-clipboard-button" type="button" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-copy" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="14" height="14" x="8" y="8" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><path d="M4 16c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V4c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h10c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2"></path></svg></button></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="chat-message group/message w-full animate-message-enter chat-message-cv" data-role="assistant" data-testid="message-assistant"><div class="flex w-full min-w-full gap-4 group-data-[role=user]/message:ml-auto group-data-[role=user]/message:max-w-2xl group-data-[role=user]/message:justify-end mt-4 mb-3"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-2"><div role="assistant" class="relative flex gap-3 hyphens-none break-words"><div class="flex w-full flex-col"><div class="relative w-full pb-8"><div data-testid="message-content"><div class="space-y-4 whitespace-normal *:first:mt-0 *:last:mb-0 chat-markdown max-w-none"><p>Για να σου γράψω τον κώδικα, πρώτα πρέπει να ξεκαθαρίσω <span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">σε τι πλατφόρμα</span> θες να τρέχει το παιχνίδι σου:</p>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Ως <span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">web game</span> (π.χ. HTML + CSS + JavaScript, παίζει σε περιηγητή)</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Ή ως <span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">ανεξάρτητο παιχνίδι</span> (π.χ. Unity σε C# ή Godot σε GDScript)</li>
</ul>
<p>Επειδή νωρίτερα είπες ότι θέλεις να είναι <span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">online σε σελίδα</span>, θα προτείνω το <span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">web version</span> με HTML/JS — που μπορείς να ανεβάσεις πανεύκολα σε host.</p>
<p>Αν το επιβεβαιώνεις, θα γράψω:</p>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm" data-streamdown="inline-code">index.html</code> (UI layout: χάρτης + μπάρα πόρων)</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm" data-streamdown="inline-code">style.css</code> (minimal design)</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm" data-streamdown="inline-code">game.js</code> (όλη η λογική: tick loop, resources, κρατίδια, μάχες)</li>
</ul>
<p>Να προχωρήσω έτσι;</p></div></div></div><div class="absolute bottom-0 transition-opacity duration-200 left-0"><div class="flex gap-1"><button class="message-action-button p-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-testid="copy-to-clipboard-button" type="button" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-copy h-[17px] w-[17px] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-200" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="14" height="14" x="8" y="8" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><path d="M4 16c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V4c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h10c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2"></path></svg></button><button class="message-action-button p-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-testid="message-upvote" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-thumbs-up h-[17px] w-[17px] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M15 5.88 14 10h5.83a2 2 0 0 1 1.92 2.56l-2.33 8A2 2 0 0 1 17.5 22H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2.76a2 2 0 0 0 1.79-1.11L12 2a3.13 3.13 0 0 1 3 3.88Z"></path><path d="M7 10v12"></path></svg></button><button class="message-action-button p-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-testid="message-downvote" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-thumbs-down h-[17px] w-[17px] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M9 18.12 10 14H4.17a2 2 0 0 1-1.92-2.56l2.33-8A2 2 0 0 1 6.5 2H20a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v8a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-2.76a2 2 0 0 0-1.79 1.11L12 22a3.13 3.13 0 0 1-3-3.88Z"></path><path d="M17 14V2"></path></svg></button></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div c