><div class="space-y-4 whitespace-normal *:first:mt-0 *:last:mb-0 chat-markdown max-w-none"><p>Για να πάρεις <span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">το link (διεύθυνση)</span> του παιχνιδιού σου, θα το δημιουργήσεις μέσα από το GitHub μετά το ανέβασμα των αρχείων.</p>
<p>Αναλυτικά τα βήματα:</p>
<hr class="my-6 border-border" data-streamdown="horizontal-rule">
<h3 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-xl" data-streamdown="heading-3">✅ 1. Δημιούργησε λογαριασμό (αν δεν έχεις)</h3>
<p>Πήγαινε στο <button data-state="closed"><a class="inline-flex h-4.5 items-center gap-1.5 rounded-md border border-border bg-background px-2.5 py-1.5 text-dark text-xs no-underline transition-colors hover:border-semidark dark:bg-paper dark:text-foreground dark:hover:border-gray-500" href="https://github.com/join" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"><span class="max-w-[180px] truncate">github.com</span></a></button> και φτιάξε ένα δωρεάν account.</p>
<hr class="my-6 border-border" data-streamdown="horizontal-rule">
<h3 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-xl" data-streamdown="heading-3">⚙️ 2. Δημιούργησε ένα νέο repository</h3>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Μετά το login, πάτα το κουμπί <span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">“New repository”</span>.</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Δώσε ένα όνομα, π.χ. <code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm" data-streamdown="inline-code">eu-clicker-conquest</code>.</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Κράτησέ το <span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Public</span>.</li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Πάτα <span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">Create repository</span>.</li>
</ul>
<hr class="my-6 border-border" data-streamdown="horizontal-rule">
<h3 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-xl" data-streamdown="heading-3">📂 3. Ανέβασε τα αρχεία σου</h3>
<p>Στην σελίδα του νέου repository:</p>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Πάτα <span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">“Add file → Upload files”</span></li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">Σύρε στο παράθυρο τα αρχεία σου:
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm" data-streamdown="inline-code">index.html</code></li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm" data-streamdown="inline-code">style.css</code></li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item"><code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm" data-streamdown="inline-code">game.js</code></li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">τον φάκελο <code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm" data-streamdown="inline-code">icons/</code></li>
<li class="py-1 [&amp;&gt;p]:inline" data-streamdown="list-item">(και το <code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm" data-streamdown="inline-code">map_europe_states.png</code>)</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<p>Μετά πάτα κάτω <span class="font-semibold" data-streamdown="strong">“Commit changes”</span>.</p>
<hr class="my-6 border-border" data-streamdown="horizontal-rule">
<h3 class="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold text-xl" data-streamdown="heading-3">🌐 4. Ενεργοποίησε το GitHub Pages</h3>
<ul class="list-inside list-disc whitespace-normal [li_&amp;]:pl-6" data-streamdown="unordered-list">
